name: Chicken Parmesan
ingredients: Chicken Breast, Salt, Pepper, Garlic Powder, Onion Powder, Flour, Eggs, Breadcrumbs, Parmesan Cheese, Marinara Sauce, Parsley
instructions: Butterfly, flatten, and season chicken with salt, pepper, garlic powder, and onion powder. Dredge in flour > egg > crumbs. Shallow fry both sides until golden brown (~4 min). Top with marinara and cheese, then broil or toast until melted. Top with parsley

name: Pan Fried Chicken
ingredients: Chicken, Salt, Pepper, Garlic Powder, Onion Powder, Paprika, Mayonnaise, Parsley
instructions: Flatten and marinate the chicken with mayonnaise. Then season both sides with salt, pepper, garlic powder, onion powder, and paprika. Pan fry in oil for about 5 minutes per side until golden brown. Top with parsley
